<div id="wikihead"><h2><a href="http://rephial.org/wiki/UserManual">UserManual</a> &gt; CharacterName</h2></div>

<div id="wikicontent"><div class="page"><h4 id="s2_1">Your Character&#39;s Name</h4><p>The final step in generating your character is to choose a name. You can type a name in on the top line of the screen, above the finalised character details, or press the * key to have the system generate a random name for you.<p>The randomly generated names are based on a list of names from Tolkien&#39;s books to give an authentic flavour.<h4 id="s2_2">Last Chance to Change!</h4><p>At the bottom of the screen, you will see the following message: <b>Esc to step back</b> (note: you can press the Esc key at any stage of the generation process to go back to the previous step), <b>S to start over</b> (go back to the beginning of the generation process; n.b. you must press S, not s), <b>or any other key to continue</b> (you are happy with your choices and character, and will accept this and begin the game).<p>If you are happy, press a key to begin the game with your character in the <a href="http://rephial.org/wiki/UserManual/TheTown">town</a>, ready to be equipped for the first venture into the dungeons of Angband.<table border="1"><tr><th align="center" width="33%">Previous Page</th><th width="33%">Up</th><th align="center" width="33%">Next Page</th></tr><tr><td align="center"><a href="http://rephial.org/wiki/UserManual/CharacterGeneration">Character Stat Generation</a></td><td align="center"><a href="http://rephial.org/wiki/UserManual">Index</a></td><td align="center"><a href="http://rephial.org/wiki/UserManual/TheTown">The Town</a></td></tr></table></div></div>

